dle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert de Avenel was born about 1360, in Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom as the son of John de Avenel and Unknown. He married Juliana Belknap in January 1387. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died from 1387 to 1402, in Salthouse, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"about 1360–From 1387 to 1402":"umbes 1360–1387 kuni 1402","1360–1402":"1360–1402","1360–1417":"1360–1417","1380–1407":"1380–1407","1335–1420":"1335–1420","–Female":"Surnud","by 1387  1st husband":"jaanuar 1387","about 1360":"umbes 1360","1402":"1402","about 1380":"umbes 1380","1335":"1335","1420":"1420","From 1387 to 1402":"1387 kuni 1402","1360":"1360","1407":"1407","1380":"1380","1417":"1417","Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom":"Lincolnshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Salt House, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Salthouse, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1360–From 1387 to 1402":"noin 1360–vuodesta 1387 vuoteen 1402","1360–1402":"1360–1402","1360–1417":"1360–1417","1380–1407":"1380–1407","1335–1420":"1335–1420","–Female":"Kuollut","by 1387  1st husband":"tammikuu 1387","about 1360":"noin 1360","1402":"1402","about 1380":"noin 1380","1335":"1335","1420":"1420","From 1387 to 1402":"vuodesta 1387 vuoteen 1402","1360":"1360","1407":"1407","1380":"1380","1417":"1417","Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom":"Lincolnshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Salt House, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Salthouse, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1360–From 1387 to 1402":"environ 1360–du 1387 au 1402","1360–1402":"1360–1402","1360–1417":"1360–1417","1380–1407":"1380–1407","1335–1420":"1335–1420","–Female":"Décédée","by 1387  1st husband":"janvier 1387","about 1360":"e